headline: Is It Too Late to Consider General Dynamics After a 29% Year to Date Surge?
summary: Wondering if General Dynamics is still worth buying after its big run, or if most of the upside is already priced in? Here is a walkthrough of what the market might be missing in the current share price. Despite a slight pullback over the last week and month, with returns of -0.6% and -1.1% respectively, the stock is still up 29.5% year to date and 24.3% over the last year, building on a 46.3% gain over 3 years and 145.3% over 5 years. Recent momentum has been shaped by ongoing defense...
